    "NLP can be used to analyze data from social media and identify pain-related experiences.",
    "NLP can analyze the language used to describe pain, assist in pain assessment and patient triage, and identify pain-related trends or patterns, with the goal of understanding, extracting, and retrieving data from unstructured written and spoken texts, such as patient descriptions of their pain experiences.",
    "NLP has been able to extract information on pain intensity, pain location, and duration from social media data (e.g., pain intensity, location, and duration) [45,46].",
